der.com%2Fhow-to-start-graphic-design-business-tools-six-figures-revenue-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudied%20graphic%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20did%20everything%20I%20could%20to%20get%20an%20internship%20at%20an%20ad%20agency.%20I'd%20leave%20direct%20mailing%20pieces%20in%20the%20foyers%20of%20multinational%20agencies%20to%20try%20to%20catch%20the%20attention%20of%20creative%20directors%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvenmoed-future-boss-50-cents-get-attention-landed-internship-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eland%20an%20internship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20final%20year%20of%20university%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20an%20unpaid%20intern%20at%20McCann-Erickson%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0b97e92-a4f8-4947-9692-df5b1f659cb5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%209%20a.m.%20to%205%20p.m.%2C%20I'd%20split%20my%20time%20between%20college%20and%20the%20advertising%20agency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evenings%20and%20on%20weekends%2C%20I'd%20work%20as%20a%20bartender%2C%20waiter%2C%20or%20barista%20to%20earn%20some%20money.%20I%20was%20working%20long%20hours%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20lucky%20to%20be%20working%20at%20such%20a%20big%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20internship%2C%20I%20put%20forward%20an%20idea%20for%20a%20Coca-Cola%20TV%20ad.%20The%20client%20loved%20it%2C%20and%20they%20even%20asked%20me%20to%20act%20in%20it%20because%20they%20liked%20my%20long-haired%2C%20dishevelled%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suddenly%20was%20getting%20a%20check%20for%20starring%20in%20the%20ad%2C%20and%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20pretty%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239a98932-5456-4786-b8cb-4c9dedddca3e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20I%20graduated%20in%202002%2C%20I%20got%20a%20full-time%20job%20with%20McCann-Erickson%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20I%20advanced%20to%20junior%20art%20director%2C%20and%20then%20