0of%20the%20cash%20withdrawals%20from%20Epstein's%20account%2C%20which%20became%20a%20catalyst%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-chase-drawn-out-breakup-with-jeffrey-epstein-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEpstein's%20messy%20breakup%20with%20JPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20after%20the%20financier%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20sex%20crimes%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20cash%20withdrawals%20should%20have%20been%20a%20bright%20red%20flag%20for%20potential%20financial%20crimes%2C%20such%20as%20money%20laundering%2C%20according%20to%20Martin%20Sheil%2C%20a%20former%20IRS%20criminal%20investigator.%20Beller's%20perspective%20might%20help%20explain%20what%20Epstein%20was%20doing%20with%20the%20money%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-epstein-pam-bondi-justice-department-investigate-jpmorgan-reid-hoffman-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20JPMorgan%20may%20have%20known%20about%20it%20at%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRich%20folks%20generally%20don't%20deal%20in%20cash%2C%20and%20banks%20know%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheil%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258e30270-083e-4550-bb62-cc17899d7a85%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cash%20withdrawals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20JPMorgan%20decided%20to%20cut%20ties%20with%20Epstein%20in%202013%2C%20bank%20officials%20said%20they%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-millions-cash-jp-morgan-accounts-lawsuit-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerned%20with%20the%20predator's%20frequent%20cash%20withdrawals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeller%20was%20often%20the%20person%20who%20physically%20withdrew%20the%20cash%20from%20Epstein's%20accounts%2C%20recently%20unsealed%20court%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20worked%20for%20Epstein%20between%201992%20and%202014%2C%20and%20his%20withdrawals%20of%20large%20amoun