y%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheil%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20have%20this%20account%20come%20in%20to%20make%20these%20large%20cash%20withdrawals%3F%20Well%2C%20what's%20the%20basis%20for%20that%3F%20That's%20not%20normal%20business%20for%20an%20investment%20advisor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20flagged%20transactions%2C%20Beller%20always%20went%20to%20the%20same%20JPMorgan%20location%3A%20270%20Park%20Avenue%2C%20the%20bank's%20headquarters%2C%20which%20CEO%20Jamie%20Dimon%20recently%20razed%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20replaced%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-jpmorgan-office-tower-270-park-avenue-gym-membership-amenities-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20office%20tower%20for%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20repeated%20visits%20to%20the%20same%20JPMorgan%20location%20should%20have%20also%20raised%20questions%20within%20the%20bank%2C%20said%20Sarah%20Krissoff%2C%20a%20former%20Manhattan%20federal%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20time%20something%20happens%2C%20or%20the%20second%20time%2C%20it%20is%20going%20to%20draw%20less%20scrutiny%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Krissoff%2C%20now%20a%20white-collar%20defense%20attorney%20at%20Cozen%20O'Connor.%20%26quot%3BAs%20something%20becomes%20a%20pattern%2C%20it%20should%20be%20raising%20more%20red%20flags.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan's%20SARs%20became%20public%20last%20month%20in%20a%20now-settled%20lawsuit%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-island-politics-stacey-plaskett-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.courtlistener.com%2Fdocket%2F66683865%2F383%2F11%2Fgovernment-of-the-united-states-virgin-islands-v-jpmorgan-chase-bank-na%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%202002%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20JPMorgan%20flagged%20for%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20that%20Beller%20had%20withdrawn%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20cash%20over%20the%20span%20of%20about%20three%20months.%20The%20report%20shows%20the%20bank%20was%20concerned%20the%20withdrawals%20from%20Epstein's%20accounts%20could%20be%20part%20of%20a%20money%20laundering%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202002%20report%2C%20Beller%20made%2016%20different%20cash%20withdrawals%20of%20about%20%249%2C800%20each%20(the%20maximum%20allowed%20was%20%2410%2C000)%20and%20cashed%20one%20%2440%2C000%20check%20from%20one%20of%20Epstein's%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeller%20%E2%80%94%20but%2C%20not%20Epstein%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20the%202002%20SAR%2C%20which%20a%20former%20FBI%20special%20agent%20hired%20by%20the%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%20to%20analyze%20the%20report%20flagged%20as%20unusual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20intention%20on%20the%20part%20of%20JPMC%20was%20to%20adequately%20report%20the%20activity%2C%20then%20the%20SAR%20would%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20himself%2C%20not%20only%20against%20Beller%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20FBI%20agent%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBeller%20was%20Epstein's%20accountant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamie%20Epstein%20private%20jet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e19b4abd5e944effb0f21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221979%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarry%20Beller%20withdrew%20cash%20from%20accounts%20associated%20with%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20private%20jet%2C%3Cp%3EUS%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20records%20show%20JPMorgan%20taking%20issue%20with%20Beller's%20cash%20withdrawals%20a%20decade%20later.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.courtlistener.com%2Fdocket%2F66683865%2F285%2F19%2Fgovernment-of-the-united-states-virgin-isl