0costs%20can't%20be%20measured%20in%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hidden%20cost%20to%20the%20epidemic%20of%20cancer%20in%20younger%20people%20is%20the%20lost%20years%20of%20productivity%2C%20socialization%2C%20and%20family%20formation%2C%26quot%3B%20Terracina%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20being%20sucked%20into%20a%20struggle%20to%20stay%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22BI%20LIFELESSONS%20CANCER%2030%20YT%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FrwDxxGFK-XildMFVD.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMethodology%3A%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%E2%80%99s%20original%20analysis%20is%20based%20on%20input%20from%20a%20panel%20of%20surgeons%20and%20oncologists%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%20Medical%20School%2C%20University%20of%20Florida%20College%20of%20Medicine%2C%20Columbia%20University's%20Irving%20Medical%20Center%2C%20and%20the%20Mount%20Sinai%20Health%20System%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20experiences%20of%2040%20cancer%20patients%20we%20spoke%20with%20for%20this%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exclusive%20dataset%20was%20compiled%20by%20health%20economists%20and%20researchers%20at%20GoodRx.%20Information%20is%20sourced%20from%20the%20Medical%20Expenditure%20Panel%20Survey%2C%20which%20provides%20the%20most%20recent%20available%20US%20health%20cost%20data.%20It%20shows%20out-of-pocket%20contributions%2C%20including%20copays%20and%20deductibles%2C%20but%20not%20insurance%20premiums.%20The%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esample%20period%20for%20MEPS%20used%20in%20this%20analysis%20is%202018%20to%202023%3B%20drug%20claims%20are%20from%20a%202024%20national%20sample%20reviewed%20by%20GoodRx.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJane%E2%80%99s%20case%2