ing%20yourself.%20That%20looks%20crazy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20attitude%20of%20entitlement%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20deserve%20this%26quot%3B%2C%20will%20always%20be%20tough%20for%20colleagues%20to%20swallow%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20employers%20who%20discourage%20work-vacation%20bundling%20might%20find%20that%20potential%20employees%20take%20notice.%20For%20a%20professional%20cohort%20who%20are%20working%20to%20live%2C%20rather%20than%20living%20to%20work%2C%20a%20business%20trip%20that's%20all%20work%20and%20no%20play%20may%20lead%20younger%20employees%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fworkplace%2F654911%2Femployee-engagement-sinks-year-low.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisengage%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20seek%20out%20more%20flexibility%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYounger%20workers%20do%20pay%20attention%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-best-employee-benefit-blind-survey-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20flexible%3C%2Fa%3E%20employers%20are.%20They%20might%20be%20drawn%20to%20companies%20that%20encourage%20experiences%20and%20don't%20micromanage%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Hudson.%20%26quot%3BYounger%20employees%20care%20about%20time-off%20policies%20and%20work-life%20balance%2C%20and%20this%20all%20fits%20into%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENasser%20concurs.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20showing%20that%20there%20are%20companies%20out%20there%20that%20do%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20if%20you're%20not%20happy%20at%20your%20company%2C%20well%2C%20maybe%20you%20should%20look%20at%20corporate%20events%20or%20a%20company%20that%20does%20allow%20you%20to%20travel.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Feve-upton-clark%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEve%20Upton-Clark%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%3C%2Fe