3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20stock%20rose%20about%203%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading%20following%20the%20results%20and%20climbed%20about%204.5%25%20after%20hours%20as%20the%20analyst%20call%20wrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFears%20of%20an%20AI%20bubble%20are%20way%20overstated%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Ives%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20senior%20equity%20research%20analyst%20at%20Wedbush%20Securities%2C%20wrote%20after%20the%20print.%20The%20tech%20bull%20called%20the%20results%20a%20%26quot%3Bpop-the-champagne%20moment%26quot%3B%20for%20tech%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20another%20validation%20point%20for%20the%20AI%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20the%20top%20of%20the%20third%20inning%20of%20this%20AI%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20analysts%20echoed%20that%20view.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThomas%20Monteiro%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esenior%20analyst%20at%20Investing.com%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20Nvidia's%20report%20shows%20the%20AI%20revolution%20is%20%26quot%3Bnowhere%20near%20its%20peak%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20both%20demand%20and%20supply%20chain%20scaling%20continuing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20concerns%20that%20ballooning%20capital%20expenditures%20%E2%80%94%20estimated%20at%20more%20than%20%24400%20billion%20across%20top%20cloud%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20slowdown%2C%20Monteiro%20said%20Nvidia's%20numbers%20show%20that%20tech%20companies%20remain%20committed%20to%20scaling%20their%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Morgan%2C%20a%20senior%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Synovus%20Trust%2C%20said%20investors%20remain%20wary%20of%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bthree%20C's%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20capex%20sustainability%2C%20circular%20financing%2C%20and%20rising%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20these%20issues%20were%20not%20put%20to%20rest%2C%20the%20recent%20print%20does%20give%20investors%20confidence%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20still%20executing%20at%20a%20high%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20Nvidia's%20results%20suggest%20those%20fears%20can%20at%20least%20be%20%26quot%3Bpunted%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20next%20quarter%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEMARKETER%20tech%20analyst%20Jacob%20Bourne%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20Nvidia%20%26quot%3Bdelivered%20another%20blockbuster%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20investors%20are%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20whether%20physical%20constraints%20%E2%80%94%20including%20power%20availability%2C%20land%2C%20and%20grid%20access%20%E2%80%94%20may%20limit%20how%20quickly%20hyperscalers%20can%20turn%20GPU%20capacity%20into%20actual%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a806d2c-c149-4ad8-bb6a-ac517c8199d3%5C%22%3E'Blackwell%20sales%20are%20off%20the%20charts'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20earnings%20call%2C%20Nvidia%20reiterated%20that%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bhalf%20a%20trillion%26quot%3B%20in%20Blackwell%20and%20Rubin%20chip%20revenue%20through%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20are%20%26quot%3Bon%20track%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20number%20will%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20Colette%20Kress%2C%20the%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20probably%20be%20taking%20more%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20new%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-nvidia-microsoft-azure-investment-deal-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20following%20its%20recent%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20would%20add%20demand.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20an%20opportunity%20for%20us%20to%20have%20more%20on%20top%20of%20the%20%24500%20billion%20that%20we%20announced%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20drew%20attention%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-net-worth-this-week2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20October%