said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20during%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20US-Saudi%20Investment%20Forum%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Trump%20made%20some%20lighthearted%20jokes%20at%20Musk's%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20so%20lucky%20I'm%20with%20you%2C%20Elon.%20I'll%20tell%20you.%20Has%20he%20ever%20thanked%20me%20properly%3F%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slow%20thawing%20of%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20comes%20after%20several%20months%20of%20intense%20public%20feuding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b7072a31-2987-428d-b54d-a5b3ab828974%5C%22%3ETimeline%20of%20the%20Musk-Trump%20feud%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Trump%20have%20had%20a%20tumultuous%20relationship%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20The%20two%20became%20steadfast%20political%20allies%20when%20Musk%20backed%20Trump's%202024%20presidential%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20then%20called%20himself%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20buddy%26quot%3B%20after%20Trump's%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20later%20headed%20the%20White%20House's%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20or%20DOGE%2C%20a%20post%20he%20left%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20soured%20in%20June%2C%20when%20Musk%20criticized%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-criticizes-trump-spending-bill-deficit-undermines-doge-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20two%20men%20started%20feuding%20publicly%2C%20with%20Musk%20saying%20Trump%20would%20not%20have%20won%20the%20presidential%20election%20if%20not%20for%20his%20support.%20Trump%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-responds-elon-musk-criticism-big-beautiful-bill-tesla-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethreatened%20to%20cut%20government%20contracts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Musk's%20companies%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20then%20said%20he%20would%20form%20a%20new%20politi