0the%20company's%20blowout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-q3-earnings-live-updates-nvda-stock-price-ai-chips-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20about%20an%20AI%20bubble%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20our%20vantage%20point%2C%20we%20see%20something%20very%20different.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20that%20powers%20nearly%20every%20major%20AI%20data%20center%2C%20that%20vantage%20point%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20that%20AI%20is%20fueling%20three%20transformative%20shifts%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20uniquely%20poised%20to%20capitalize%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20stems%20from%20the%20slowdown%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoores-law-almost-over-transistors-stop-shrinking-after-2021-semiconductor-industry-association-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMoore's%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20trend%20that's%20seen%20computer%20chips%20double%20in%20power%20roughly%20every%20two%20years.%20As%20that%20progress%20stalls%2C%20companies%20are%20shifting%20from%20traditional%20chips%20to%20GPUs%2C%20which%20Nvidia%20specializes%20in%20building%20to%20power%20AI%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20also%20cited%20the%20rise%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20transforming%20search%20and%20recommendations%20at%20companies%20like%20Meta.%20Finally%2C%20he%20cited%20the%20shift%20to%20agentic%20AI%20and%20physical%20AI%E2%80%94which%20power%20coding%20assistants%20and%20robotics%E2%80%94as%20other%20game-changing%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%20is%20chosen%20because%20our%20singular%20architecture%20enables%20all%20three%20transitions%20and%20does%20so%20for%20any%20form%20and%20modality%20of%20AI%20across%20all%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%2